vote.title: A public hearing to receive comments and to approve an ordinance granting a request to change the name of Audrey Street, between Agnes Street and Greenbay Street, to “Dimple Jackson Street” - NC212-008 - Financing: New street blades to be prepared and paid for by the City of Dallas (see Fiscal Information for potential future costs)
